Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da ake bayarwa ta mai jiran gado na Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma mai zarginsa da cin zarafin mata da ke cewa an yi shi ne a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, rikice-rikicen siyasa ya ci gaba, inda masu watsa labarai na talabijin suka soke shirin ranar Juma'a a minti na karshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi da FBI don gudanar da bincike kan zarginsa a cikin mako guda.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin sulhu na majalisar dattawa cewa yana da tabbacin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa barazanar shan giya kuma ya yi kokarin cire masa tufafinsa a wani bikin makaranta.
Kavanaugh, wanda shi ne mai ba da shaida a kan wannan batu, ya ce ya san cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka yi rahoton cewa sun kalli wannan bidiyon a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin yana lissafin matsakaicin masu kallo na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai nan take ba daga wasu tashoshin talabijin da suka nuna shaidar ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da tambayoyi game da yawan masu kallon shirye-shirye a ofis.
Don a bayyana shi, mutane ne masu girman kai kamar waɗanda ke cikin gasar ko kuma waɗanda ke gabatar da kyautar Academy.
Nielsen ya ce:  Tashar Fox News Channel, wadda ke da masu masaukin baki da suka goyi bayan Kavanaugh, ta fi sauran tashoshin talabijin da yawan masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin zaman da aka yi a ranar.
ABC ce ta fara kallon shari'ar da mutane miliyan 3.26.
Nielsen ya ce: CBS ta kalli miliyan 3.1, NBC ta kalli miliyan 2.4, MSNBC ta kalli miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN ta kalli miliyan 2.52.
