Lokacin da yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi takararsa a cikin wani hadari da ya faru a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin ayyukan Trump guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da yin takara a wurare da dama da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ba a gudanar da zaben tabbatar da shugabancin kotun koli ba, Trump na neman goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar watan Nuwamba, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rashin ikon majalisa a lokacin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a yi zaben Trump a West Virginia yau da dare kuma ta yaya za a kalli shi a yanar gizo?
An shirya gudanar da yakin neman zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare ET, ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar intanet ta hanyar hanyar sadarwa ta YouTube.
Trump na iya yin magana game da sauraron sauraron sauraron wanda zai zama shugaban kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a wannan makon, wanda ya kara tsanantawa saboda zargin rashin adalci na jima'i inda aka dage zaben tabbatar da shi a majalisar dattawa saboda binciken FBI.
Amma babban abin da ake nufi a wannan yakin shine a taimaki 'yan Republican su yi tsayayya da babban zaben na watan Nuwamba domin su ci gaba da samun karfi.
A cewar Reuters, masu gudanar da yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce, za a gudanar da zaben na mako guda domin "karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu fafutuka a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma samun kuri'un da suka fi na 'yan majalisar dattawa da na wakilai".
"Samun iko da majalisa na da muhimmanci a shirinsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da tashin hankali".
An shirya gudanar da yakin neman zaben a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, wanda zai iya jawo masu gwagwarmaya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a buga su a jaridun Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kuri'u sama da 40 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, ya shaida wa Reuters cewa: "Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban zai zo don taimaka masa wajen samun kuri'u ba".
