Jarumin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya yi tir da rashin mutuncin al'umma
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin jerin wasannin da aka yi na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan, mai shekaru 31, ya yi tir da nuna bambanci da ake yi wa jarumin, yana mai cewa wasan yana nufin cewa matasa suna jin cewa dole ne su yi ƙarfi don samun girmamawa.
Da take magana da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta ce ta yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ya ɓace' kuma ta yi mamakin yadda za ta magance matsalar rashin daidaiton maza yayin da aka fara hanyar sadarwa ta mata mai suna #Me.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'mai karfin gaske' game da magance matsalar.
"Na ji kaina yana jin tsoro, na ce, 'Ina waɗannan mugayen ayyukan maza suke zuwa?'
'Shin za mu iya koyar da maza a lokacin da suka girma game da matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yau?'
