Kwayar cutar HIV/AIDS: China ta ce akwai karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari
China ta samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HIV da masu fama da cutar AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar bisa ga jami'an kiwon lafiya.
Kusan sabbin mutane 40,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a rabin shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sabbin kamuwa da cutar sun samo asali ne daga hulɗa da ba na jama'a ba, wanda ya bambanta da yanayin da ya gabata.
A wasu yankunan kasar Sin, cutar ta HIV ta fi yaduwa ta hanyar bayar da jini mai cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ta hanyar wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da masu kamuwa da cutar kanjamau a China yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na da matukar damuwa ga masu yin jima'i tsakanin maza da mata a China.
An dakatar da yin jima'i tsakanin mutane na jinsi daya a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna wariya ga masu yin jima'i tsakanin mutane iri daya na karuwa.
A cikin al'ummar da ke bin al'adun gargajiya, bincike ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza masu yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin kamuwa da cutar na faruwa ne ta hanyar yin jima'i ba tare da kariya ba a cikin wannan dangantakar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar kanjamau a matsayin wani bangare na maganin cutar.
