A ranar Asabar ne wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani daga cikin ma'aikatanta ya fitar da bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar wakilai na Republican a shafukan lauyoyi na Wikipedia.
Wani dan Democrat a Los Angeles ya ce ana ta karawa masu gudanar da muhawara da kuma masu neman zabe "ta hanyar goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican".
Waters ya ce a cikin wani sakon Twitter cewa: "Rashin gaskiya, karya, karya ce mai ban tsoro".
Rahoton da aka bayar ya kunshi adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham daga South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu daga Utah.
Rahoton da ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya bayar a Capitol Hill a yayin da ake sauraron karar da majalisar dattawa ta yi kan zargin lalata da ake yi wa wanda aka nada a matsayin mai gabatar da kara a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan labarin ya fito ne bayan da wasu sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Hill ya ce:  Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun bayyana cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke nuna inda bayanan suka fito yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayanin ɗaya daga cikin ma'aikatan Waters.
"Wannan zargin ba shi da tushe kuma ba gaskiya ba ne, ƙarya ce kawai", in ji Watera.
"Daya daga cikin ma'aikatana, wanda aka yi wa barazana a kan mutuncinsa, bayanansa na sirri da kuma tsaronsa saboda zargin yaudara da karya; ba shi da alhakin fitar da wannan bayanin.
Waɗannan zarge-zargen ba su da tushe kuma ba gaskiya ba ne, ƙarya ce kawai".
Maganar Waters ta jawo suka a shafukan intanet, ciki har da na tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar shugaban kasa Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer ya ce: "Wannan ƙin yarda yana da ban haushi".
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ya son zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, ya kamata ya yi haƙuri.
Bai kamata ya ƙi yin aikinsa ba.
Kada ya tambaye ni abin da mai zarginsa ya zarge shi.
Ya kamata ya yi shiru kuma ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya tilasta masa ya yi la'akari da yadda Waters ya amsa tuhumar ne saboda 'yan Democrat sun soki Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka zarge shi da nuna rashin jin daɗi a shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Zai zama abin mamaki idan gaskiya ne", in ji ta a shafinta na Twitter.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da "hukumomi da hukumomin da ke da alhakin shari'a suna binciken abin da ya ce yaudara ce.
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "Za mu yi kokarin ganin an gano duk wadanda suka aikata hakan", kuma za su yi hukunci bisa ga doka game da duk wani mummunan aiki da suka yi ko kuma mummunan aiki ga duk wani ma'aikaci da ke aiki a wurina.
Binciken fim din Johnny English Strikes Again - Rowan Atkinson mai wasan kwaikwayo mai ban sha'awa
Yanzu, ya zama al'ada a duba sakamakon ficewar Burtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai, wanda ya zama kamar sabon fim game da Ingilishi kuma yana da alama cewa sabon fim ɗin na cikin jerin fina-finai da aka sani da Johnny English yana da rikici da wasan kwaikwayo; wanda ya fara a 2003 a matsayin Johnny English sannan kuma ya sake fitowa a 2011 a matsayin Johnny English Reborn.
Wani fim mai kama da wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo game da batun da ba shi da ma'ana wanda zai nuna damarmu a matsayin ƙasa a cikin damar fitarwa?
A kowane hali, wani ɗan wasan kwaikwayo mai tsufa, mai tsufa mai suna Johnny English ya sami damar sake yin fim na biyu, wanda ya fi dacewa da shi a matsayin babban wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo ga mutanen da ba su iya Turanci ba.
Tana taka rawa a matsayin wakili mai zaman kansa wanda ke koyon yadda za a yi dariya don nuna kamannin Clouseau, wanda ya zama kamar Mr. Bean a wasan da ya kai ga kammala gasar cin kofin Olympics na 2012 a London.
Asalin, wanda ya dogara ne akan al'ada da kuma jarumi Atkinson wanda ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan tallan gidan talabijin na Barclaycard TV wanda yanzu ya manta da shi, ya bar shi da ban mamaki.
Akwai yanayi biyu masu kyau a cikin fitowar JE.
Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English ya kusanci jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da rigar kare kai ta 500 da kuma yadda takobin jirgin sama ya taɓa jakarsa.
Kyautar Atkinson ta yin wasan kwaikwayo ta jiki tana da kyau sosai, amma baƙar fata tana da ƙarfi kuma ba ta da kyau a cikin yanayin da ke cikin yanayin da ya dace musamman a cikin fina-finai masu suna kamar 007 da Mission Impossible inda 'yan wasan kwaikwayo "suna san abin da suke buƙata" suna yin wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin ƙarin.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa ga yara fiye da manya kuma ba a ba da izinin Johnny English ba kuma ya fi mayar da hankali ga fina-finai da Atkinson ya yi wanda ba ya furta kalma a matsayin Bean.
Labarin da aka fi yawan karantawa shi ne cewa Biritaniya tana cikin haɗari.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin babbar kungiyar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, ya gano bayanan duk wani dan leken asiri na Burtaniya da ke aiki a wurare daban-daban, inda aka nuna wani dan wasa a matsayin mai aiki amma abin takaici an ba shi rawar Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shine babban abin da ya faru ga babban firaministan da ke da sha'awar zama dan siyasa mai matukar sha'awa, wanda ke cikin ruwa mai sanyi: Emma Thompson tana da kyakkyawan matsayi a matsayin Teresa-May amma ba ta da wani abu mai mahimmanci a cikin rawar da ta taka.
Masu ba shi shawara a harkokin kasuwanci sun gaya masa cewa an fallasa ɗan leƙen asiri a ko'ina, kuma dole ne wani ya yi ritaya.
Kuma hakan yana nufin babu wani kamar Johnny English, wanda a lokacin yana da aikin koyarwa a wata babbar makaranta, amma yana koyar da darussan da ba na makaranta ba game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: Wannan shawara ce mai kyau a wurin English wanda yake koyar da darussan a makarantar Rock School game da leƙen asiri.
An dawo da Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall inda dole ne ya sami umarni na gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Yanzu Bough ya yi aski, kuma ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwan karkashin ruwa, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ke rike da shi amma ba ta da amfani.
Don haka Batman da Robin suna wasa da abubuwa masu ban tsoro a cikin Sabis na Sirri na Sarauniya, suna haɗuwa da wata mata mai ban tsoro wacce ke aiki a Olga Kurylenko mai suna Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, ministan ya yi kasafin kudi don ya shiga tarkon wani mai fasahar zamani mai karfin kudi wanda ke ikirarin cewa zai iya magance matsalar matsalar kwamfuta a Burtaniya: wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jason Volta, da kuma Jake Lacy.
English ya fara tafiya mai wuya na ɓoyewa: suna yin baranda, suna sarrafa gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna yin ɓarna a cikin jirgin ruwa mai tsada mai suna Volta; kuma English ya nemi ya ɗauki alhakin kansa lokacin da ya yi ƙoƙarin yin amfani da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu ban mamaki don yin horo a cikin gidan Volta.
Duk wannan yana faruwa a ƙarshen fim, amma kamar yadda yake da ban sha'awa da kuma mahimmanci, akwai gidan talabijin na yara da ke nuna duk wannan.
Hakan na da kyau sosai.
