Jam'iyyar Kwadago ta musanta cewa tana tunanin shirin aiki na kwanaki hudu a mako ga 'yan Birtaniya da ke samun albashi na kwanaki biyar
Jeremy Corbyn na jam'iyyar Labour yana tunanin wani babban tsari wanda zai bar dukkan 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma a biya su kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni daban-daban su nemi yadda za su adana kuɗi ta hanyar haɓaka ilimin kere kere (AI) don ma'aikata don samun ƙarin ranar hutu.
Hakan zai iya sa ma'aikata su ji daɗin hutun mako na kwana uku, amma a biya su kuɗin da suka saba samu.
Masu bayar da rahoto sun ce wannan shawarar ta 'dace' da shirin 'yancin tattalin arziki da kuma shirin sauya yanayin da zai amfane ma'aikatan kasar.
An yi sauye-sauyen kwanaki hudu a mako wanda ya samu goyon bayan jam'iyyar kwadago ta kasa a matsayin hanyar da za ta sa ma'aikata su yi aiki da kyau a kan sauye-sauyen tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa, 'Ana sa ran za a fitar da wani tsari na bita kafin karshen shekara.
'Ba abu ne da zai faru a rana ɗaya ba amma aiki kwana huɗu a mako yana da kyau a matsayin hanyar da za ta dace da tsarin tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin masana'antu gaba ɗaya.'
Jam'iyyar Labor ba zata kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, yayin da jam'iyyar kare muhalli ta yi alkawarin aiwatar da aikin kwana hudu a cikin babban kamfen din zaben 2017.
Koyaya, a halin yanzu ba duk membobin jam'iyyar kwadago ke goyon bayan wannan bukatar ba.
Mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar ya ce, "aikin kwana hudu a mako ba wani shiri ba ne kuma ba za a yi tunaninsa ba.
Mataimakin shugaban kasa, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour da ya gudana a makon da ya gabata don bayyana matsayinsa kan sauyin tattalin arziki na gurguzu.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar dawo da ikon da aka kwace daga "masu mulki marasa ganuwa" da kuma "masu shiga cikin kamfanonin ruwa, gas da wutar lantarki".
Shirin mataimakin shugaban kasar ya kuma nuna cewa abokan hulda a kamfanonin samar da ruwa na iya rashin goyon bayan shirinsa gaba daya yayin da gwamnatin ma'aikata ta 'yanta kudaden' bisa la'akari da munanan ayyukan da ta lura da su.
Ya kuma bayyana cewa yana shirin sanya ma'aikata a cikin kwamitin gudanarwa na kamfanoni da kuma kafa Asusun Gudanar da Masu Amfani da Masu Amfani da su wanda zai ba da kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari ga kamfanonin masu zaman kansu, inda ake tsammanin kowane mutum zai iya samun ribar riba har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy sun fadawa shirin "60 Minutes" ko binciken FBI kan Kavanaugh zai iya canza tunaninsu
Binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben shugaban kasa na mako guda, kuma ana tambayar ko binciken da hukumar ta samu zai iya janye goyon bayan 'yan majalisa na Republican.
A wani hira da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, mai gabatar da shirin "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI na iya samun wani abu da zai sa su canza ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina jin daɗi.
Kennedy ya ce, "Hakika haka".
"Na yi magana game da shiga shari'a, na yi magana, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Sai na kira shi bayan wannan, na ce masa, 'Ka yi haka?'
Ya cika alkawarinsa, ya yi iya ƙoƙarinsa kuma ya ba da cikakken bayani".
Amma, kamar dai an riga an ƙayyade zaɓen Graham.
"Na yanke hukunci game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma ina so in yanke hukunci kan tuhumar da ake masa".
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta hakan", Graham ya kara da cewa yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ya ce ba zai iya tantance shi ba.
Wannan tuhuma ta shekara 36 kenan.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da zai iya canja yanayin".
Ko bikin al'adun duniya ya yi tasiri wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa wanda ya kunshi manyan mawaƙa da ke da burin kawar da talauci a duniya.
A yanzu shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival yana jan dubban mutane zuwa babban lawn na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin ayyukan manyan masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don yin gwagwarmaya don ainihin burin bikin wanda shine kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
An kafa bikin Global Citizen a shekarar 2012, a matsayin wani ci gaba ga shirin Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya na kasa da kasa da ke ba da shawara kan yadda za a kawar da talauci da kuma kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don samun tikitin kyauta zuwa bikin (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin masu daraja), masu halartar taron dole ne suyi ayyuka daban-daban ko "ayyuka" kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika imel ga shugabannin duniya, yin kira ko wasu hanyoyi masu amfani don taimakawa wajen yakin neman neman neman talauci.
Amma ta yaya ne shirin Global Citizen zai kai ga cimma burin da aka yi shekaru 12 kafin a cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin biyan mutane su je wajen yin wasan kwaikwayo kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta sa mutane su nemi a yi aiki ko kuma wani irin "tallafin kan layi" ne wanda mutane ke ganin za su iya kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu a takardar neman izini ko aika saƙo ta Twitter?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya rubuta "ayyuka" miliyan 19 da magoya bayansa suka yi, da suka shafi manufofi daban-daban.
Shafin ya ce wannan ya taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su fitar da manufofi da tsare-tsare masu darajar dala biliyan 37 da nufin inganta rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta yi alkawarin aiwatar da ayyuka 390 inda aka bayar ko aka tara kimanin dala biliyan 10.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa tallafi da aka samu ya kawo canji kai tsaye ga mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu daga cikin abubuwan da suka hada da hadin gwiwa da The Power of Nutrition, kungiyar 'yan kasuwa da masu gudanar da ayyukan Birtaniya da suka yi alkawarin "taimaka yara su cika iyawarsu", sun yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun samu sama da sakonni 4,700 na Twitter da Global Citizens suka wallafa.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasashe da kuma Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya kawo karshen rashin daidaiton zamantakewar da ya zama tarihi", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan kungiyar The Power of Nutrition, a wani taron da aka yi a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an gabatar da shawarwari sama da 5,000 na inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta tallafawa shirin da ake kira The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da za su sami tallafin abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a dandalinsa, ya ce: "Me ya sa kake tsammanin za mu iya kawar da talauci?"
Kungiyar Global Citizen ta amsa da cewa: "Zai kasance hanya mai tsawo da wahala; wani lokacin kuma ta ƙunshi gazawa da kuma cimma burin.
Amma, kamar yadda manyan juyin juya halin kare hakkin bil'adama da na nuna wariyar launin fata a Afirka ta Kudu suka kasance kafin mu fara aiki, za mu kai ga ci gaba, domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Masu kida da suka hada da Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin wadanda za su yi waka a wannan shekara a bikin da za a gudanar a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su jagoranci.
Amurka na iya amfani da jiragen ruwa na yaki don "kullewa" da kuma hana Rasha fitar da makamashi, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida ya ce
Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" ta yi amfani da jiragen ruwanta na yaki don hana iskar gas ta Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da dama, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda jaridar Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya zargi Rasha da shiga cikin yakin Siriya, wanda ya kasance a matsayin gayyatar gwamnati, amma a matsayin hujja saboda yana son neman sabon tushen iskar gas.
An ruwaito cewa ya ce: "Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son samun damar samun damar sayen gas kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai".
Kuma bisa ga abin mamaki da hukumomi suka ce, akwai hanyoyi da kuma damar magance su.
"Amurka tana da ikon, ta hanyar jiragen ruwanta, ta bude hanyoyin ruwa, kuma idan ya zama dole, ta rufe su, don tabbatar da cewa iskar gas din ba ta kai kasuwa ba".
Zinke zai yi jawabi ne a taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da iskar gas" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda gwamnatin Washington ke hulda da Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa babu wani kwatankwacin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki na Iran da Rasha shine, a nan gaba, don samun makamashi da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana nufin Rasha "doki ne mai wayo" wanda tattalin arzikinsa ya dogara da man fetur.
Wannan furucin ya zo ne bayan da gwamnatin Trump ta shirya kara yawan iskar gas da ake amfani da ita a Turai, inda za ta maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ke sayar da iskar gas a kan farashi mai rahusa ga kasashen Turai.
A sakamakon haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, sun yi kokarin janye Jamus daga aikin samar da iskar gas da ake kira Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya sanya Berlin ta zama "garkuwa" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta ci gaba da bayyana cewa, dala biliyan 11 na aikin samar da iskar gas da ake kira Nord Stream 2, wanda ake sa ran zai ninka karfin da ake da shi na samar da iskar gas zuwa murabba'in biliyan 110, ba komai ba ne face aikin tattalin arziki.
Kremlin ta ce rashin amincewar da Washington ta yi da shirin ya samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na nuna son kai a kasuwar.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayin cewa gas ba zai iya zama kayan aiki na nuna bambanci ba kuma masu amfani da shi dole ne su sami damar zaɓar waɗanda za su magance shi", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawar da ya yi da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Jamus ba ta yi maraba da matsayin Amurka ba, inda ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji shiga cikin batun tsauraran matakai a cikin Tarayyar Turai da yarjejeniyar Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da matukar damuwa idan wata kasa ta uku ta shiga cikin tsarin isar da iskar gas", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) a taron da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi "tunani sosai" game da takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata Massachusetts
A ranar Asabar ne Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce ta "yi tunani sosai" kan yadda za ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron jama'a a gidan majalisa na Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin tsayawa takara.
A cewar jaridar The Hill, ta ce: "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington kuma su sake kafa gwamnatinmu mai rarrabuwa inda mata za su yi mulki".
"Bayan 6 ga watan Disamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a cikin jawabinsa a majalisar dattawa, yana mai cewa "yana tura kasar zuwa hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya".
Warren ya sake yin tir da Trump da kuma wanda ya nada shugaban kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A cikin sakon Twitter na ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce: "Hakika muna bukatar FBI ta gudanar da bincike kafin zaben".
Koyaya, kuri'ar da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ta nuna cewa mafi yawan masu jefa kuri'a a yankin Warren ba su yi tunanin ya kamata ya tsaya takara a 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin da takwas cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a "masu iya" a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata sanata ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar wani bincike da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk ta gudanar da ita.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan ya tsaya takara.
Ya samu goyon baya sosai daga tsohon Gwamna Deval Patrick, inda kashi 38 cikin 100 suka amince da shi ya tsaya takara, kuma kashi 48 cikin 100 suka ki.
Wasu manyan 'yan Democrat da ake tattaunawa da su a kan neman takarar zaben 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai iya yanke shawara a cikin watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da rikicewar Track Palin a cikin yakin neman zaben Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki domin ya shiga jerin sunayen wadanda za su je a watan Satumba.
