Shirin rediyo na Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji 'ƙanƙantar da kansa' game da jima'i
Dan wasan ninkaya na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin an wulakanta shi saboda yanayin jima'i, amma ya sami kwarin gwiwa saboda ya samu nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 24 ya ce bai san hakan ba har zuwa lokacin da ya shiga makarantar sakandare inda ya fahimci cewa "ba kowa bane kamar ni".
A lokacin da take magana a shirin rediyo na 4 mai suna Desert Island Discs da Lauren Laverne, ta ce ta yi magana game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba wa wasu "bege".
Ta kuma ce kasancewa mahaifiyar ta sa ta daina tunanin samun lambar yabo a gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin na dogon lokaci, Kirsty Young, ta yi watanni da yawa ba ta da aiki saboda rashin lafiya.
