"Har zuwa yau, wannan jin kasa da bambanci ya kasance babban abin da ya ba ni ƙarfi da ƙarfin da zan iya cimma burina", in ji ta.
Yana son ya nuna cewa shi "wani abu ne", ya faɗi haka don kada kowa ya yi mamaki idan ya sami labarin jima'i.
Dan wasan da ya lashe lambobin tagulla biyu a wasannin Olympics ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar gay kuma ya yi amfani da halartar wasannin Commonwealth da ke yankin Ingila a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da dama da su daina yin laifukan yin jima'i da juna.
Ya ce ya fitar da shi ne saboda yana jin yana da damar samun damar rayuwa cikin 'yanci ba tare da damuwa ba kuma yana son ya ba wa wasu "tabbatarwa".
Gwarzon dan wasan kwallon kafa mai lashe kofin duniya sau uku ya ce saduwa da mai shirya fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black a shekarar 2013 "abin mamaki ne a gareshi".
Daley ta auri wanda ta lashe Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekaru 20 a shekarar da ta gabata amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka sha wahala da yawa, kai matashi ne", a nan ya ce ya halarci wasannin Olympics na farko yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan kwana uku, yana mai cewa yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya sha wahala.
Abokan sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni, inda suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, wanda Daley ya ce "dukkan tunaninsa" ya canza.
Ya ce, "Idan kun tambaye ni a bara abin da na fi so, zan ce, 'Ina son lashe lambar zinare.'
"Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi lambobin zinariya na wasannin Olympics muhimmanci.
"Madalar da na ci a gasar Olympics ita ce Robbie".
An sa wa ɗanta suna bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da cutar kansa ta kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai taba yarda da cewa zai mutu ba kuma cewa ba abin da ya tambaye shi ba ne tikitin su zuwa gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London; domin yana son su zauna a gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, 'Baba ba za ka iya zama a wurin zama na gaba ba.'
