Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai bukaci karin kwalliya don kauce wa rashin nasara.
Mickelson, wanda ke buga gasar ta shekara-shekara ta 12, ya zama dan wasa na biyu a matsayin kyaftin din Jim Furyk a wasan kwallon kwando hudu da 'yan wasa hudu suka yi a ranar Asabar.
