Sabon jirgin yakin Jamus ya sake juyawa lokaci
An ba da sabon jirgin ruwan yaki na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan da aka yi amfani da su a lokacin yakin sanyi, amma ba za a samu ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingancin tsarin da kuma tsada, kamar yadda kafofin watsa labarai na cikin gida suka ruwaito.
An dage ba da izinin shiga teku ga "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwa na sabon nau'in Baden-Wuerttemberg, har zuwa farkon 2019, a cewar Die Zeit da ke ɗauke da wata sanarwa da mai magana da yawun sojin ya bayar.
An samu wasu jiragen ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalar jigilar su ta kawo cikas ga wannan babban aikin.
An umarci jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da ke cikin rundunar sojan ruwa a 2007 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Tabbas, dole ne ya kasance yana da makamai masu ƙarfi, nau'ikan makamai masu linzami daban-daban da na jiragen ruwa da kuma fasahar shiga cikin ruwan abokan gaba ba tare da an yi amfani da shi ba, kamar rage radar, siginar hasken rana da ji da na'urorin daukar sauti.
Wani muhimmin fasalin jirgin ruwa shine cewa an sake gina shi a cikin dogon lokaci, saboda haka ya kamata a iya samun sabbin jiragen ruwa a cikin teku aƙalla shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin ruwa.
Duk da haka, jinkirin na nufin jiragen ruwa masu fasahar zamani, wanda aka ce zai iya ba da damar ci gaban hanyar Jamus, ba za su kasance a cikin yanayin ba idan aka fara amfani da su, in ji Die Zeit.
Jirgin ruwan F125 ya yi ta taho a cikin jaridu a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da jirgin ruwa ga kamfanin da ya kera shi bayan an cire shi daga jirgin.
Babu cikakken bayani game da dalilin da ya sa aka sake dawo da jirgin, amma jaridar Jamus ta ce manyan kurakurai da dama a cikin "shirye-shirye da na'ura" sun hana jirgin daga shiga yakin.
Musamman, kurakuran shirye-shirye sun kasance masu mahimmanci yayin da jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki tare da rukunin jiragen ruwa 120, wanda shine ɓangare na rukunin jiragen ruwa na tsohuwar jirgin ruwan Bremen.
Kuma, jirgin ya zama mai nauyi sosai wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya rage ƙarfin sojojin ruwa ta hanyar ƙarin abubuwan da aka sabunta a cikin kwanakin nan.
Jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7000 ya ninka na jirgi iri daya da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga na'urorin da suka lalace, farashin duk aikin, gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, zai zama matsala.
An ce ya kai Yuro biliyan 3.1 (Amurka dala biliyan 3.6), daga Yuro biliyan 2.2 da aka tsara.
Matsalar sabbin nau'ikan jiragen ruwa ta sake bayyana ne a yayin da aka yi ta ba da rahoto cewa sojojin ruwa na Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokoki ta Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa na Jamus a halin yanzu "sun kasa samun jiragen ruwa da za su iya kai hari".
Ya ce matsalar ta ci gaba da ƙaruwa a tsawon shekaru, domin tsoffin jiragen ruwa sun daina tafiya a teku kuma ba a taɓa samun wasu da za su maye gurbin su ba.
Ya yi gunaguni cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da ya shiga rundunar sojan ruwa.
