Fita daga EU Brexit: Birtaniya 'na iya yin nadama har abada' bayan rashin masana'antar kera motoci
Birtaniya "za ta yi nadama har abada" kan yadda ta rasa matsayinta na babbar mai kera motoci a duniya bayan ficewarta daga Tarayyar Turai, in ji Sakataren Kasuwanci Greg Clark.
Ya kara da cewa "yana da matukar damuwa cewa kamfanin kera motoci na Toyota na Burtaniya ya shaida wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, za ta dakatar da kera motoci na wucin gadi a masana'antar ta da ke Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
"Muna bukatar mu fahimci juna", in ji Clark.
Kamfanin kera motoci na Japan ya ce sakamakon jinkirin kan iyakar da zai iya faruwa idan ba a cimma yarjejeniya ba a lokacin da Burtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai zai haifar da asarar ayyuka.
Kamfanin Burnaston, wanda ke kera motocin Toyota Auris da Avensis, ya kera motoci kusan 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata, wanda kashi 90% na motocin da aka fitar zuwa kasashen Tarayyar Turai.
Marvin Cooke, shugaban kamfanin Toyota da ke Burnaston ya ce: "Na yi imanin cewa idan Birtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai a karshen watan Maris, za a samar da motoci a masana'antarmu".
Sauran kamfanonin kera motoci a Burtaniya sun nuna fargabar ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, wanda ya hada da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover.
Alal misali, BMW ta ce za ta rufe wani karamin masana'anta a Oxford wata daya bayan Birtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai.
Babban abin damuwa shi ne masana'antun kera motoci sun ce suna samun kayan aiki ne ta hanyar sayar da kayayyakin da ke cikin matsala a cikin rashin daidaito bayan ficewar Burtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai.
Kamfanin Toyota na aiki kan "rage lokacin kera motoci", inda ake samun kayan aiki kowane minti 37 daga masu kera motoci a Burtaniya da Tarayyar Turai don kera motocin da aka shigo da su.
Lokacin da Burtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga Maris, za a iya dakatar da ayyukan a kan batun da kamfanin ke cewa zai iya haifar da jinkiri da kuma asarar kayan aiki.
Ba zai yiwu ba Toyota ta ajiye motocin da aka kera a rana guda a cikin shagonta da ke Derbyshire, in ji kamfanin kuma hakan na iya kawo karshen samar da motocin.
Mista Clark ya ce shirin Theresa May na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ya shafi dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasashen Turai da kuma Turai, "wanda aka gyara sosai don kaucewa yin amfani da iko a kan iyakoki".
"Ya kamata mu cimma yarjejeniya. "A cikin hira da shirin Today na BBC Radio 4 ya ce, "Muna son cimma yarjejeniya mai kyau wanda zai ba mu damar cimma burinmu a wannan kakar kawai amma kuma zai ba mu damar samun damar".
"A bayyane yake cewa ba kawai a Toyota ba har ma da sauran masana'antun kera motoci inda muke buƙatar ci gaba da ingantaccen tsarin samar da kayayyaki da kuma samar da kayayyaki masu inganci".
Toyota ba ta iya tantance lokacin da za ta daina kera motoci ba, amma a cikin dogon lokaci, ta yi gargadin cewa karuwar sayayya za ta rage gasa a kasuwa kuma ta rage yawan ayyukan yi.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston na tsawon shekaru 24 kuma memba ne na kungiyar ma'aikatan masana'antar, ya ce membobinsa na ci gaba da nuna damuwa: "A ganina, idan aka cire wasu ayyuka, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
"Ya kamata mu samar da tsari mai inganci da tabbaci game da makomar dangantakarmu da Tarayyar Turai", in ji mai magana da yawun gwamnatin.
Taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya sake jinkirta, in ji Ofishin Shugaban Amurka
Babban taron Donald Trump da mataimakin shugaban kasa Rod Rosenstein na iya "a dage shi zuwa mako guda" yayin da ake ci gaba da takarar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaba a matsayin babban jami'in rigakafin, in ji Ofishin Shugaban Amurka a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein na kula da aikin mai ba da shawara kan harkokin siyasa Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma bakin Rasha a zaben, hulda tsakanin masu goyon bayan Trump da Rasha da kuma yadda shugaban ya hana shari'a yin aikinta.
Ko Trump zai kori babban jami'in harin, da kuma yadda hakan zai shafi 'yancin Mueller, ya zama abin da ake ta zage-zage a Washington tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya yi magana da kayan sauraron sauti don yin rikodin tattaunawar da ya yi da Trump da kuma yiwuwar a yi wa shugaban kasa zagon ƙasa bisa ga kwaskwarimar 25 ga Tsarin Mulki na Amurka.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan sanarwa.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya je ofishin shugaban Amurka, kuma akwai jita-jita cewa zai iya yin murabus.
Maimakon haka, an sanar da taron da Trump zai yi a hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke New York a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce "ya fi son" kada ya kori Rosenstein amma yanzu an dage taron da ya kamata ya yi domin ya guji ganawa da kwamitin sulhu na majalisar dattawa kan shari'ar da Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da aikata laifuka na jima'i, Dr Christine Blasey Ford, suka yi.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya bukaci FBI ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya kara jinkirta zaben da za a yi a majalisar dattawa.
Sakatariyar yada labarai ta Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a tashar Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
Da aka tambaye shi game da taron da Rosenstein ya yi, ya ce: "Ba a amince da ranar ba, watakila wannan watan, ko kuma a sake ta mako guda saboda wasu abubuwan da ke faruwa a kotun koli.
Amma duk za mu ga yadda hakan zai kasance kuma zan ci gaba da kawo sabbin labarai ga kafofin watsa labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida ba su yarda da wannan rahoton ba: Sanders bai gayyaci taron a ofishin shugaban Amurka ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai masaukin baki Chris Wallace ya yi mamakin dalilin.
Sanders ya ce rashin samun labarai ba saboda ƙin 'yan jaridar talabijin ba ne "saboda rashin halayensu", duk da cewa ya ce: "Na yarda da cewa suna da halayensu".
Ya kuma ce sadarwa kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da kafofin yada labarai na karuwa.
"Shugaban kasa ya fi kowa a gabansa yawan tambayoyi da amsa tambayoyi", in ji shi, ya kara da cewa: "Mun duba wadannan alkaluman".
Ana ci gaba da tattaunawa kan labarai, a cewar Sanders, amma "idan kafofin watsa labarai sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, zai fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sau da yawa kuma kun ga muna yin hakan a cikin 'yan makonnin da suka gabata kuma zai dauki lokaci don sabuntawa lokacin da zaku iya magana da shugaban Amurka.
A al'ada, ana tambayar Trump yayin da yake barin fadar shugaban Amurka ko kuma yayin da yake halartar ganawa da kuma taron manema labarai da manyan jami'ai.
Ba a yawan samun damar tattaunawa da kafofin watsa labarai shi kaɗai.
A wannan makon a birnin New York, shugaban ya bayyana dalilin da ya sa, inda ya saba wa doka kuma a wasu lokutan ya bayyana a gaban taron manema labarai.
