Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jami'ai suka ruwaito, inda ake sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Yayin da tsarin sadarwa da na sadarwa suka kasa aiki, jami'an agaji ba su samu damar samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, wanda ke arewacin Palu kusa da inda girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afku.
A Palu, an ceci mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu birni ne a lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kusa da gabar tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, inda aka kiyasta yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana tunawa da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ya faru shekaru 40 da suka gabata.
Donggala yanki ne mai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 km) da ke bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin yanki ne na yanki, wanda aka kiyasta yawansa 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da kiwo sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki a lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman, a yankin da ke kusa da gabar tekun Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a cikin lardin, amma mafi yawan ayyukan ma'adinai suna faruwa ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da girgizar kasa sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Kasa ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya afka a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan wani yanki na Pacific kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, rabin su 'yan asalin Aceh ne.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a bakin tekun Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, da ke bakin teku a Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa tsibirin Java ta Kudu, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya halaka kusan mutane 700 a gaɓar tekun kudu.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa wani yanki kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, daga Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, inda ta yi sanadiyar lalacewa da kuma barazana ga al'umma, kamar yadda aka yi a lokacin da aka yi tsunami a shekarar 2004.
Ba a taɓa samun tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon ambaliyar.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, kuma ta yi ta fama da arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido ba tare da gidaje na ɗan lokaci ba.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, bisa zargin cin zarafin jama'a.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata fyade a cikin gida, ta gurgunta sanarwar cin zarafin cikin gida kuma ta ki amincewa da kama ta, a cewar wani rahoto da jami'an tsaro na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mata da suka saba ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don sanar da su laifin da ake zarginta, sai suka kwace wayar.
Palin yana tsare a gidan yarin Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma ya biya kudin belin da bai kai dala 500 ba, kamar yadda KTUU ta ruwaito.
An gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa "bai yarda da zargin ba" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko ya yarda da zargin, kamar yadda gidan talabijin ya ruwaito.
An zargi Palin da laifuffuka guda uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda da kuma tarar da dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin laifi mai sauƙi na Class B, wanda ake azabtar da shi da ɗaurin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da tarar dala dubu biyu.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin da aikata laifuka ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge ta da laifin cin zarafin mahaifinta, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda domin ta sanar da su game da harin.
A yanzu haka ana shari'arsa a gaban kotun tsaron Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge ta da aikata laifukan cin zarafin cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoto kan laifin da aka aikata a cikin gida da kuma shan giya yayin da take shan magungunan da suka shafi laifin.
Yarinyar da yake so ta yi masa ba'a.
An kori Sarah Palin daga rukunin tsoffin sojoji a 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankali na ɗanta da tashin hankali na zuwa yaki a Iraki.
