An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da amfani da motar haya ta kamfanin Home Depot don yin harbi a kan hanyar keke a kan babbar hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu tuka kekuna a kan hanyar a watan Oktoba.
