Dukkanin laifuffukan na iya kaiwa ga hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, kotun kolin kasar ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22 da suka hada da kashe mutane takwas da suka hada da taimakawa wajen karbar kudade, wanda kuma masu gabatar da kara suka yi amfani da shi wajen gurfanar da masu laifi da kuma zargin aikata mugunta da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma shiri sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da "harin da ya fi na kowa, mai ban tsoro da kuma mummunan aiki".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya ji rauni, ya azabtar kuma ya kashe dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar da ya yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu a harin 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun wuce tun lokacin da Kotun Yankin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu 'yan kasuwar miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu amma daga baya aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Hukuncin kisa na baya-bayan nan a cikin shari'ar jihar a New York ya kasance a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke musu hukunci bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin leken asiri ga tsohuwar Tarayyar Soviet shekaru biyu kafin yakin Cold.
An kashe Rosenbergs a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna cewa bai yi nadama ba game da ayyukansa a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji daɗi game da abin da ya yi, kamar yadda 'yan sanda suka ruwaito.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya yi tunanin kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ta'addanci ta ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar takardar da ke dauke da tuhumar da ake masa.
Ya kuma bukaci a nuna tutar kungiyar ta'addanci ta ISIS a dakin asibitin da yake kwance, kamar yadda 'yan sanda suka ruwaito.
Ya yi adawa da tuhumar da aka yi masa a kan laifuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "ya yi matukar damuwa" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa ne maimakon a yi masa shari'a a kan laifin da ake tuhumarsa da kuma yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da wata hanyar samun 'yanci ba, wanda zai kara damun duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar da ke kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da su daina bayyana yadda za a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin Tory ya ce ya kamata a bai wa NIGEL FARAGE mukamin tattauna ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin 'karfafawa' jama'a gwiwa a yau a wajen zanga-zangar da za a yi a wurin taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Ukip ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su bar 'inuwa' saboda sukar da ake yi wa Tarayyar Turai, inda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar dokokin Theresa May ta ce ya kamata ta dauki nauyin tattaunawa da Tarayyar Turai.
Dan majalisa mai zaman kansa Peter Bone ya shaida wa masu halartar taron a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya 'ta fice daga cikin kungiyar' yanzu da Mista Farage zai zama sakataren fitar da Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai.
Amma matsalar da Mrs May ta fuskanta ita ce ta hada kan abokan aikinta da suka yi watsi da ra'ayin da ke nuna cewa 'yan Tory na EU suna son su ci gaba da zanga-zangar ficewar Birtaniya daga EU a cikin birane.
Firayim Minista yana fama da samun shirinsa na ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai a kan lokaci yayin da yake fuskantar hare-hare daga masu neman ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai da kuma masu neman ta ci gaba da zama a Tarayyar Turai.
'Yan takarar sun ci gaba da cewa zai ci gaba da kokarin neman sasantawa da Belgium duk da rashin karbuwa, kuma sun matsa masa kan ya soki Tarayyar Turai da jam'iyyar kwadago domin su yanke shawara kan al'amurran da suka shafi su da kuma matsalolin su.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa masu halartar ziyarar Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son 'dawo da shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai'.
Ya ce ya kamata a saka Mr Farage a cikin wannan shirin kuma a ba shi aikin tattaunawa da Belgium.
Ya ce, 'Da a ce shi ne shugabanmu, da mun riga mun fita.'
'Zan yi kira ga Birtaniya ta fice daga EU amma muna bukatar mu soke shirin Birtaniya na fice daga EU,' in ji wani dan majalisa mai wakiltar Wellingborough.
Da yake magana a kan matakin da ya dauka a kan Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi ba don nuna kasawarmu.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi tir da bukatar jama'a tun bayan zaben 2016: 'Ra'ayin cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin kungiyar ba gaskiya bane.'
'Yar jam'iyyar Tory mai neman ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai, Andrea Jenkyns, wacce ke cikin ziyarar, ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: 'Ina so in ce kawai: Firayim Minista, ka saurari jama'a.
'Tasirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ba shi da kyau a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi zabe a kai ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu kuma masu neman sauyi da muke aiki tare da su suna kan titi ne da ke sa mu zaɓa a farko.
Ka bar wannan shirin kuma ka fara sauraronsa.'
A wani sako mai kama da wannan da aka aika wa Mrs May, ta ce: 'Firai ministan ya ci gaba da aiki idan ya cika alkawuransa.'
Mista Farage ya gaya wa 'yan siyasa da ke kan tafiya cewa dole ne su ji 'inuwa' idan za su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
'Yanzu abin da ya rage shi ne amincewa tsakaninmu, jama'a da kuma bangaren siyasa.'
'Za su yi kokarin hana Birtaniya fice daga Tarayyar Turai kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa 'ba za mu taba yarda da cewa ba za a hukunta ku ba.'
A cikin wani sako ga taron jama'a, ya ce: 'Ina son sanya bangaren siyasarmu, wanda ke shirin yin makirci ga shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai, a cikin inuwa.
'Muna kira ga jama'a da su kare kasar nan da ta ba mu nasara wajen fitar da Burtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun yi aiki, a karkashin jagorancin Burtaniya, tare da alfahari da Burtaniya.'
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ci gaba da kasancewa cikin ƙungiyar sun yi tafiya zuwa Birmingham kafin su tsaya na sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Masu fafutukar kawo sauyi sun yi ta taho da tutar jam'iyyar Tory suna adawa da ficewar Burtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai bayan da suka kaddamar da jam'iyyar a karshen mako.
'Yan jam'iyyar Labour, ciki har da Lord Adonis, sun soki tsoffin masu bin ka'idoji kan matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta a kan shirin jam'iyyar yayin da aka fara taron.
Ya kara da cewa: 'Waɗannan su ne mutanen da ke gaya mana cewa muna da fasahar zamani kuma duk fasahar Kanada ta ci gaba, iyakokin da ba su da haraji, da kuma kasuwancin da ke kan iyaka da Ireland.'
'Ba gaskiya ba ne.
Babu abin da ya fi sa'ad da aka kori Ingila,' in ji shi.
Warren ya shirya yin 'tunani sosai' kan takarar shugaban kasa
A kan Sanata Elizabeth Warren, ta ce "za ta yi la'akari sosai da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan dimokiradiyar Massachusetts din ya yi jawabi a wani babban taro a yammacin Massachusetts ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ke sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, yana takarar neman takara ta biyu a watan Nuwamba, inda ya yi takara da Geoff Diehl, mataimakin shugaban yakin neman zaben Trump a Massachusetts a 2016.
An yi jita-jita cewa zai iya yin hamayya da Trump a 2020.
A taron da ya gudana a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taronsa na 36 da ya yi da masu jefa kuri'a a cikin mazabarsa ta hanyar tsarin majalisa tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani da ya halarci taron ya tambaye shi ko yana son ya zama shugaban ƙasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa: "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su kafa gwamnatinmu da ta rabu biyu, inda mata za su yi sarauta".
An kama wani a harin da ya kashe dan wasan LSU Sims
A ranar Asabar, 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge, La., sun sanar da cewa an kama wanda ake zargi da aikata wannan ta'asa a cikin harin da ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar dan wasan kwando na LSU, Wayde Sims.
Rundunar 'yan sandan Baton Rouge ta sanar da kama mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, mai shekaru 20, da misalin karfe 11 na safe, lokacin da aka sanar da hakan a kafafen yada labarai.
Sun wallafa bidiyo game da fashin da aka yi a ranar Juma'a, suna neman mutane su taimaka musu su gano mutumin da ke cikin hotunan.
An harbe Sims, mai shekara 20, a kusa da Jami'ar Kudancin kasar a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya mutu sakamakon harbin bindiga da aka yi masa a kai kuma ya mutu a wurin", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul, a cikin wata sanarwa ga manema labarai a ranar Asabar, kamar yadda 247sports ta ruwaito.
Wayde ya zo ne don ceton abokinsa kuma Simpson ya kashe shi.
An tuhumi Simpson kuma ya yarda cewa yana wurin harbin da bindiga kuma ya yarda cewa ya harbi Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wata matsala ba kuma an kai shi gidan yari na sashen 'yan sanda na East Baton Rouge.
Matashin dan wasan mai tsayi biyu a Baton Rouge, Sims ya buga wasanni 32 inda ya fara 10 a bara kuma ya kai kimanin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da sake dawowa 2.9 a wasa daya.
Gasar motar Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusa lashe kofin duniya bayan da kungiyar ta tabbatar da cewa shi ne ya lashe gasar da Sebastian Vettel
A bayyane yake tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya samu damar buga gasar a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa Mercedes ta tabbatar da cewa tana da babban matsayi a gasar.
Tun daga farkon gasar, Bottas ya fara da kyau kuma ya kusa cin Hamilton yayin da ya yi gwagwarmaya don samun matsayi a cikin zagaye biyu na farko kuma ya sa Vettel ya yi wa abokin takararsa harbi.
Vettel ya je wurin gyaran tayoyin motar da farko kuma ya bar Hamilton a baya, wanda ya zama abin da aka yanke shawara.
Motocin Mercedes sun yi kyau kuma sun zo bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya ci gaba bayan ya yi karo da Ferrari kuma mai kula da motar ya yi kuskure wanda ya bar rata kuma ya hana shi gwagwarmaya a cikin kusurwa ta uku.
Max Verstappen ya fara ne daga baya a kan sauran motocin kuma ya zo na bakwai bayan tseren farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Ya jagoranci mafi yawan tseren yayin da yake motsawa a kan ƙafafunsa don ya ci gaba da tseren ta hanyar wuce Kimi Raikkonen a matsayin na huɗu.
Ya kuma kai gajin motar a layin 44 amma bai samu damar kara saurinsa ba a layin takwas na karshe inda Raikkonen ya zama na hudu.
Ranar tana da wuya sosai domin Valtteri ya yi aiki sosai a ƙarshen mako kuma ya zama mutum mai kyau.
Hamilton ya ce: "Kungiyar ta yi aiki mai ban mamaki don samun na farko da na biyu".
Wannan mummunan magana ne.
Shugaban kasar Donald Trump ya soki Sanata Dianne Feinstein a lokacin da take takarar shugabancin kasar a ranar Asabar saboda ta dage cewa ba ita ce ta wallafa wasikar da Christine Blasey Ford ta rubuta da ke zargin wanda za a nada a matsayin shugaban kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, da cin zarafinta ta hanyar jima'i.
Da yake jawabi a yakin neman zaben na West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa ba, amma ya yi da'awar cewa abin da ya faru a majalisar dattawa ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne, masu mugunta, da rashin aminci".
Ya ce, "Abu daya da zai iya faruwa kuma mai kyau shi ne abin da ya faru a 'yan kwanakin nan a majalisar dattawa, inda kuke ganin fushi, abin da kuke ganin mutane masu fushi da mugunta da mugunta da rashin aminci".
"Idan ka duba abubuwan da aka wallafa ba tare da izini ba, to, za ka ce, 'A'a, ban taɓa yin hakan ba.
Ban yi hakan ba".
Ka Tuna da Shi?
Dianne Feinstein, ka taɓa yin wannan wallafa ba tare da izini ba?
Ka tuna amsarsa . . . ka taɓa buga wannan labarin ba tare da izini ba: "eh, eh, me?
A'a, ba haka ba.
Ban taɓa yin ba".
Yana da kyau, sai dai kadan.
Mun riga mun fitar da shi ba tare da izini ba...A'a, ba mu taba fitar da shi ba tare da izini ba", in ji shi, don faranta wa sanata rai.
An aika wa Feinstein wasika mai bayanin zargin da Ford ya yi wa Kavanaugh a watan Yuli, kuma an fitar da shi ba tare da izini ba a farkon watan Satumba, amma Feinstein ya yi tir da sakin da ofishinsa ya yi ba tare da izini ba.
"Ban taba boye zargin Dr. Ford ba, ban taba yin wani abu ba, ko kuma na sanar da labarin da ya yi", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin, kamar yadda jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Ya ce in yi asirin kuma na yi kamar yadda ya ce".
Amma a bayyane yake cewa shugaban bai karɓi ƙin yarda ba, wanda ya yi sharhi a cikin yakin neman zaben na ranar Asabar da dare: "Zan gaya muku, wannan mummunan magana ne.
Wataƙila ba ya yi hakan, amma shi ne mafi munin furcin da na taɓa gani".
Da yake ci gaba da kare kansa da tsohon shugaban Kotun Koli, wanda aka zargi da laifin lalata da mata uku, shugaban ya ce 'yan Democrat za su yi amfani da zargin don amfanin kansu.
"Sun ƙudura niyya su sake samun ƙarfi a kowace hanya.
"Suna ganin mugunta, zalunci, ba su damu da wanda za su iya cutar da shi ba, wanda za su iya cin zarafinsa don samun iko da kuma yin iko".
Gasar Elite League: Dundee Stars sun doke 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a wasan da Giants suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun gyara nasarar da suka samu a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League yayin da suka kara da Belfast Giants kuma suka lashe wasan neman kwangilar 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci kwallaye biyu da wuri a kan kwallaye biyu da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka buga.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun yi nasara a wasan kafin Dwyer ya sake sa Giants a kan ragamar.
Francois Bouchard ya ci kwallo daya da Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da Adam Keefe ya ci nasara a gasar Elite League a kakar wasa, inda ya ci Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu a kakar wasa da kungiyoyin biyu suka kara, inda Giants suka lashe wasannin farko uku.
Dwyer ya ci kwallo na farko a minti na uku da talatin da biyar da Kendall McFaull, inda David Rutherford ya ci Beauvillier da kwallo na biyu bayan 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
A wani abu da ya zama kamar fara wasan, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan cikin wasa a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya jefa Cownie don cin nasara a 15:16 na wasan.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba da jagorantar wasan a farkon rabin lokacin da ya ci kwallo na biyu a wasan da yamma a ƙarshen rabin.
Kungiyar da ta karbi bakuncin wasan ta sake yin kwallo, kuma Bouchard ya sake cin kwallo a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi kokari don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar cin kofin farko na wasan kafin rabin rabin kuma ya tabbatar da cewa tawagarsa ta ci wasan a minti na karshe.
Giants, wadanda yanzu suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su ziyarci Milton Keynes a wasan na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da jirgin ya mutu don ya tabbatar da cewa daruruwan fasinjojin sun tsira daga girgizar kasa
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia da za a yi masa lakabi da jarumi bayan ya mutu a kokarin tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama mai dauke da daruruwan mutane ya sauka lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma da yawa sun bace bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa ta karshe mai karfin gaske ta ci gaba da afkawa yankin kuma mutane da dama sun tsere daga barakar gine-gine a garin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun tsira, wani matashi mai shekaru 21 mai suna Anthonius Gunawan Agung ya ki barin aikinsa a wani hasumiya da ta yi ta girgiza sosai bayan guguwar da ta afkawa tashar jirgin sama ta Mutiara Sis Al Jufri a Palu.
Ya ci gaba da aikinsa na tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air Flight 6321, wanda ya isa inda aka kama wuta, zai iya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar da yake ganin za ta rushe.
Ta mutu a asibiti.
Kakakin hukumar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ta Indonesia Yohannes Sirait ya ce matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, kamar yadda ABC News ta Australia ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan, don mu kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici, ya mutu a cikin wannan jirgin kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
Ta daɗa cewa: "Mun yi baƙin ciki sosai da muka ji hakan".
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai yayin da hukumar kula da bala'i ta ce ba a kai ga garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong ba.
Kakakin hukumar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, ya ce: "Lambobin na ci gaba da karuwa tun lokacin da aka rufe gawarwakin mutane da dama, yayin da aka bar sauran mutane da dama da ba a kai ga su ba".
Ruwan sama mai tsawon mita shida ya lalata Palu inda ake sa ran binne wasu a makabartar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen saman soji da na sufuri suna kawo kayan taimako da kayan aiki.
Risa Kusuma, mai shekaru 35, ta shaida wa Sky News cewa: "A kowane minti ana samun jami'an agaji da gawawwakin mutane.
Ruwa mai kyau yana da wuya.
An yi fashi a dukan wuraren da ake sayar da kayayyaki".
Jan Gelfand, daraktan agajin agaji na kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa ta Red Cross a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta Indonesia tana neman yadda za ta taimaka wa wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
"Abin ya riga ya zama mai haɗari, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo, ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku duka ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk wani aikin ceto.
Kun shirya?" in ji CNN.
A farkon wannan shekarar, girgizar kasa ta afkawa Indonesia a Lombok inda ta kashe sama da mutane 550.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Yanzu, kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce mutum daya ya bace bayan ya fadi a cikin wani tafki
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ya yi hatsarin jirgin a bakin tekun Pacific a Micronesia yanzu ya ce mutum daya ya bace, bayan da aka ce an kwashe dukkan fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin sama 47 daga inda jirgin ya nutse.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa cewa a ranar Asabar da yamma, ba ta iya gano mutumin ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin tsakiya, asibitoci da masu bincike don gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa ba nan da nan ga bukatar da aka yi na samar da ƙarin bayani game da shekarun ko kuma asalin fasinjan.
Jiragen ruwa na yankin sun taimaka wajen ceto wasu fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya fadi a ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a tsibirin Chuuk.
Hukumomi sun ce an kwantar da mutane bakwai a asibiti a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma duk suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Dalilin hatsarin shi ne, ba a bayyana abubuwan da suka faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da Sojojin ruwan Amurka sun gano cewa jirgin ya fadi a cikin kwari jim kadan bayan hanyarsa.
Wasu shaidu sun yi imanin cewa jirgin ya yi kuskure wajen duba hanyar.
Wani abokin aikinsa na Amurka, Bill Jaynes, ya ce jirgin ya sauka a ƙasa sosai.
Jayness ta ce, "Wannan abu ne mai kyau".
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun tsere cikin ruwan da ya yi musu rauni kuma suka isa inda aka yi musu gaggawa daga jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma sun yi kururuwa kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
Rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka ta ce masu aikin jirgin ruwa da ke kusa sun yi amfani da jirgin ruwa mai kama da jirgin ruwa don taimakawa wajen ceto don samun mutane zuwa gabar teku kafin jirgin ya nutse kusan mita 30 (100) a cikin ruwa.
Bayanai da cibiyar tsaro ta jirgin sama ta Aviation Safety Network ta bayar sun nuna cewa mutane 111 ne suka mutu a hadarin jirgin sama a kamfanonin jiragen sama da aka rubuta a PNG a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata amma babu wanda ya mutu a jirgin Air Niugini.
Mai bincike ya gano lokacin da aka kona matar da rai
A ranar Asabar ne dai masu gabatar da kara suka sake gabatar da karar wani mutum da ake zargi da kona wata mata a Mississippi a 2014.
A ranar Laraba ne ma'aikacin ma'aikatar shari'a na Amurka Paul Rowlett ya gabatar da shaidar sa'o'i da dama a matsayin gwani a binciken da aka yi a wurin da aka aikata laifin.
Ya nuna wa majalisar yadda ya yi amfani da wayar salula wajen yin bincike kan tafiye-tafiye daban-daban da ake yi tsakanin wanda ake zargi mai shekaru 29 mai suna Quinton Tellis da kuma wanda ya kashe mai shekaru 19, Jessica Chambers, a daren da aka kashe ta.
