Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 inda ta doke Kungiyar Amurka a wasan karshe da maki 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a gasar Le Golf National da aka yi a wajen birnin Paris na kasar Faransa.
A halin yanzu, Amurka ta ci nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake dawo da kambin bayan da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don kayar da Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala sosai a gasar, ya jefa kwallonsa cikin ruwa a rami na 3 a 16, inda ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya lashe gasar a duk wasannin, ya zama dan wasa na 1 a cikin 4 da ya ci nasara fiye da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi 5&4 inda ya ci kwallo kadan a kan dan wasan Turai Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya, ya ci 2-1 a wasan da Ian Poulter na Ingila ya buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Tsohon dan wasan da ya taka leda a gasar Ryder Cups, dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan da ya lashe kofin Turai da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma a yau, ina da abin da zan yi.
Wannan shekara ce mai muhimmanci.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas don ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin ciki da na dawo da kofin.
Game da kungiyar ne kuma ina farin cikin cewa na iya taimakawa", in ji Garcia cikin farin ciki bayan lashe gasar Turai.
Ya bar abokin wasansa John Ram wanda ya doke Tiger Woods da 2 sets 1 a wasan daya-daya a ranar Lahadi.
"Na yi girma ina kallon wannan girman da na samu na doke Tiger Woods", in ji Rahm, dan shekara 23.
Woods ya sha kashi a wasanni hudu da suka gabata a Faransa kuma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wani babban adadi shi ne, daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan da suka lashe kofuna 14 a duniya, wanda ya fi Jack Nicklaus girma.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi ta tazarar karshen mako don ganin ta samu damar daidaitawa da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka yi wasan golf a matakin da ya fi na kowacce gasa.
Kyaftin din tawagar Amurka, Jim Furyk, ya ce bayan wasan da bai yi wa tawagarsa dadi ba, "Ba na alfahari da 'yan wasan da suka yi gwagwarmaya sosai.
A wannan safiya, muna matsawa kungiyar Turai a wani lokaci.
Mun rarraba.
Muna godiya sosai ga Thomas.
Kyaftin ne mai kyau.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Za mu sake haduwa a matsayin tawagar, zan yi iya kokarina don zuwa gasar PGA ta Amurka da kuma Kwamitin Gasar Ryder Cup kuma za mu yi nisa.
Ina son 'yan wasan 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftininsu.
Ya kamata ka shawarci kyaftin dinka.
Mun fi yin wasa".
Sabuntawa game da jan guguwa: Rage yawanta a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Sabbin rahotanni daga Hukumar Kula da Kifin Kifi da Dabbobin Florida sun nuna cewa akwai raguwar yawan kwayar cutar a yankunan Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, za a iya samun 'yan wasa masu tasiri a wasu yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier; wanda ke nufin cewa akwai raguwar mayar da hankali kan wasan.
Kyakkyawan Red Tide ya ƙara kusan mil 210 na bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin lardin Lee.
Ana iya samun wuraren a cikin nisan kilomita 25 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma an sami 'yan wurare kaɗan a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama mai jan wuta a lardin Pasco.
An samu daidaiton rinjaye a cikin ko a gefen tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan rinjaye da kuma a gefen tekun Hillsborough County, rinjaye a cikin Manatee County, tare da rinjaye a cikin ko a gefen tekun Sarasota County, rinjaye a cikin Charlotte County, rinjaye a cikin ko a cikin Lee County da rinjaye a cikin Collier County.
Matsalar numfashi na ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu wani batun numfashi da aka ambata a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
